headline: ADM Declares Cash Dividend
summary: CHICAGO, May 07, 2025--ADM’s (NYSE: ADM) Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend of 51.0 cents per share on the company’s common stock. The dividend is payable on June 11, 2025, to shareholders of record on May 21, 2025.

headline: ADM to Present at 2025 BMO Farm to Market Conference
summary: CHICAGO, May 07, 2025--ADM (NYSE: ADM) will present at the 2025 Farm to Market Conference on Wednesday, May 14, in New York. The company will participate in a fireside chat at 10:15 a.m. Eastern Time.
